<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>News</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.9.4/Chart.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  </head>
  <body>

    <div id="upper-bar">
      <div class="link" id="one"><a href="/">Cattle</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="two"><a href="/shed">Shed</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="three"><a href="/grazing">Grazing</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="four"><a href="/milk">Diary Output</a></div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <h1>Daily Diary Data</h1>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="text-part">
      <p>Real time data is sent from various sensors installed within the cattle shed at regular intervals. Measurements are taken 5 times a day and responsive actions are automatically implemented daily to ensure that shed conditions remain at peek.</p>
      <% if(error) { %>
        <%= error %>
      <% } %>
      <b>Average Measurements of Today:</b>
      <br>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Output</b></li>
        <li>Total Milk Output: <%= totalMilkOutput %></li>
        <li>Total Cattle Weight: <%= totalCattleWeight %></li>
        <br>
        <li><b>Problems</b></li>
        <li>Animals with below average milk output:
          <% for(var i = 0; i < problematicMilkOutput.length; i++) { %>
            <%= JSON.stringify(problematicMilkOutput[i]) %>
          <% } %></li>
        <li>Animals with below average or above average weight: 
          <% for(var i = 0; i < problematicCattleWeight.length; i++) { %>
            <%= JSON.stringify(problematicCattleWeight[i]) %>
          <% } %>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
  </body>
</html>